description: Cyber Security 1 AB engages in the provision of cyber security solutions. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 146 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-09-22. The company provides risk and compliance services, consulting, implementation and ongoing operation and review of cybersecurity solutions, conducting operations from Sweden, South Africa, the United Kingdom, Kenya, Germany, Austria and the United Arab Emirates. The firm delivers services to public and private sector organizations, including government, healthcare, retail, insurance, manufacturing and hospitality sectors. The services comprise client audit, penetration testing, application security assessment, information systems audit, security monitoring, urgent incident response & crisis management, data leakage & loss prevention, as well as data security & management. The Company’s main shareholders are Barclays Bank and UBS Switzerland AG.
